    Simple navigation service implementation that loads objects from the Site Plan. Supports populating node data via a dedicated method that can be overridden to load any data that is required, as long as it can be presented as a TemplateAsset. Reads the full site plan tree in one query, but only reads asset data for nodes that it is going to actually return.
